ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[As of 17 Jul 2020, the total number of cases of COVID-19 confirmed in Iran is 269 440, including 13 791 deaths, an increase of 2379 cases and 183 deaths since 16 Jul 2020. According to another media report there are now 8 provinces with the highest incidences of COVID-19 in the country (Khuzestan, Razavi Khorasan, East and West Azerbaijan, Mazandaran, Golestan, Bushehr, and Hormozgan) and an additional 6 provinces at high risk (Tehran, Fars, Kerman, Alborz, Kohgiluyeh, and Boyer-Ahmad; https://www.aa.com.tr/en/asia-pacific/iran-reports-over-180-more-virus-fatalities/1913846).

